    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weird Wormholes is a casual game about traveling through wormholes to try and get back home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your ship to mine planets for resources and process these resources into components to enable your travels or to trade with local Space Stations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local Space Stations will sell you upgrades to speed up and assist you in your endeavors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The idea behind the game is centered around a relaxing and casual game play. There is no way to die or loose, just more efficient ways of doing tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3328020/extras/d331029664edbca6a235b2ece1263e9d.avif?t=1735554462\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In-game features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mine planets for resources</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Refine resources using your ships onboard smelter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use refined resources to manufacture items to enable you travels through wormholes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trade with local space stations to upgrade your ship</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Several purchasable incremental-like generators you can invest in to passively improve your ship</p></li></ul>",
